001package org.biopax.ols.impl;
002
003import java.io.Serializable;
004import java.util.Collection;
005
006import org.biopax.ols.DbXref;
007import org.biopax.ols.Term;
008import org.biopax.ols.TermSynonym;
009
010/**
011 * @author R. Cote
012 * @version $Id: TermSynonymBean.java,v 1.1 2006/03/23 12:32:41 rglcote Exp $
013 */
014public class TermSynonymBean implements TermSynonym, Serializable {
015
016    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
017
018    /**
019     * <p>Represents ...</p>
020     */
021    private String parentTermPk;
022
023    /**
024     * <p>Represents ...</p>
025     */
026    private Term parentTerm = null;
027
028    /**
029     * <p>Represents ...</p>
030     */
031    private String synonym = null;
032
033    /**
034     * <p>Represents ...</p>
035     */
036    private String synonymPk;
037
038    /**
039     * <p>Represents ...</p>
040     */
041    private String synonymTypePk = null;
042
043    /**
044     * <p>Represents ...</p>
045     */
046    private Term synonymType = null;
047
048    /**
049     * <p>Represents ...</p>
050     */
051    private Collection<DbXref> synonymXrefs = null;
052
053    /**
054     * @return
055     */
056    public Term getParentTerm() {
057        return parentTerm;
058    }
059
060    /**
061     * @param _parentTerm
062     */
063    public void setParentTerm(final Term _parentTerm) {
064        parentTerm = _parentTerm;
065    }
066
067    /**
068     * @return
069     */
070    public String getSynonym() {
071        return synonym;
072    }
073
074    /**
075     * @param _synonym
076     */
077    public void setSynonym(final String _synonym) {
078        synonym = _synonym;
079    }
080
081    public String getSynonymPk() {
082        return synonymPk;
083    }
084
085    public void setSynonymPk(String synonymPk) {
086        this.synonymPk = synonymPk;
087    }
088
089    public String getSynonymTypePk() {
090        return synonymTypePk;
091    }
092
093    public void setSynonymTypePk(String synonymTypePk) {
094        this.synonymTypePk = synonymTypePk;
095    }
096
097    /**
098     * @return
099     */
100    public Term getSynonymType() {
101        return synonymType;
102    }
103
104    /**
105     * @param _synonymType
106     */
107    public void setSynonymType(final Term _synonymType) {
108        synonymType = _synonymType;
109    }
110
111    public Collection<DbXref> getSynonymXrefs() {
112        return synonymXrefs;
113    }
114
115    public void setSynonymXrefs(Collection<DbXref> synonymXrefs) {
116        this.synonymXrefs = synonymXrefs;
117    }
118
119    public String toString() {
120        String syntype;
121        if (synonymType != null)
122            syntype = synonymType.getName();
123        else
124            syntype = "unknown";
125        return "[Synonym]: " + synonym + "(" + syntype  + ")";
126    }
127
128    public String getParentTermPk() {
129        return parentTermPk;
130    }
131
132    public void setParentTermPk(String parentTermPk) {
133        this.parentTermPk = parentTermPk;
134    }
135
136    public boolean equals(Object o) {
137        if (this == o) return true;
138        if (!(o instanceof TermSynonymBean)) return false;
139
140        TermSynonymBean that = (TermSynonymBean) o;
141
142        if (parentTermPk != null ? !parentTermPk.equals(that.parentTermPk) : that.parentTermPk != null) return false;
143        if (synonym != null ? !synonym.equals(that.synonym) : that.synonym != null) return false;
144        if (synonymPk != null ? !synonymPk.equals(that.synonymPk) : that.synonymPk != null) return false;
145        if (synonymTypePk != null ? !synonymTypePk.equals(that.synonymTypePk) : that.synonymTypePk != null)
146            return false;
147
148        return true;
149    }
150
151    public int hashCode() {
152        int result;
153        result = (parentTermPk != null ? parentTermPk.hashCode() : 0);
154        result = 31 * result + (synonym != null ? synonym.hashCode() : 0);
155        result = 31 * result + (synonymPk != null ? synonymPk.hashCode() : 0);
156        result = 31 * result + (synonymTypePk != null ? synonymTypePk.hashCode() : 0);
157        return result;
158    }
159}
